## Navigation & Auth Flow Gaps

| Gap | Impact | Fix |
|-----|--------|-----|
| Session lost on hard reload | 🔴 High | Add `sessionStorage` persistence to [SessionContext](file:///d:/Code%20Learning/WebP/SecretVault/securevault/frontend/src/app/SessionContext.tsx#18-23) |
| Footer shows on app pages (dashboard/settings/profile etc.) | 🟡 Medium | Hide footer on app routes via `usePathname` |
| Navbar: no active-state highlighting for current page | 🟡 Medium | Add `usePathname` → highlight active nav link |
| Some nav links open with `<a>` not `<Link>` → hard reload possible | 🟡 Medium | Audit all `<a href>` usages |
| Profile shows mock fingerprint not real key | 🟡 Medium | Use `session.publicKey` to derive fingerprint |
| Messages/Audit-log use 100% mock data | 🟡 Medium | Wire Firebase / backend API |

